title: Bug 116609 [Regression] Color orange doesn't work.
description: Bug 116609 [Regression] Color orange doesn't work. Description: Color orange doesn't work.
OB: When selecting the color orange in the preview, the expected result is that the orange color should be applied.
EB: However, the actual result is that the orange color is not applied.
SR: Steps to reproduce: 1. Open the preview. 2. Select the color orange from the color options. 3. Verify if the orange color is applied correctly.
